WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.283
"-Hi everybody!
-Hello!"

00:00:02.283 --> 00:00:07.558
Today we're going to play with the color-changing Maho no Magic Tea Set!

00:00:07.558 --> 00:00:14.725
The cake and sweets change colors when they warm up!

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:16.283
Let's open it up!

00:00:20.191 --> 00:00:22.625
The brush feels like a towel!

00:00:22.625 --> 00:00:26.291
Welcome! What can I get you?

00:00:26.291 --> 00:00:32.000
"-I'd like a strawberry cookie and some shortcake!
-Ok, thank you!"

00:00:32.008 --> 00:00:34.991
"-Here you are!
-They look delicious!"

00:00:35.033 --> 00:00:36.583
Itadakimasu!

00:00:37.475 --> 00:00:39.716
I love strawberries!

00:00:41.783 --> 00:00:44.708
Now I wanna try something different…

00:00:44.708 --> 00:00:47.091
Ok, please wait a minute!

00:00:47.091 --> 00:00:49.691
And now for some magic!

00:00:52.449 --> 00:00:57.125
The pink cookie changed to purple!

00:00:57.133 --> 00:00:59.199
It's a tasty blueberry cookie!

00:01:01.316 --> 00:01:04.341
This one changed to chocolate cream!

00:01:04.383 --> 00:01:07.949
Welcome! What can I get you?

00:01:07.983 --> 00:01:11.566
I'd like a mint cream donut and some tea please.

00:01:11.566 --> 00:01:13.441
Sure!

00:01:13.441 --> 00:01:15.875
Time to pour the tea!

00:01:20.149 --> 00:01:23.200
Wow, it turned brown!

00:01:24.133 --> 00:01:28.199
"-Thanks for waiting!
-It looks so good!!!"

00:01:28.233 --> 00:01:32.558
Itadakimasu! … But I wanna try another flavor!

00:01:32.558 --> 00:01:37.475
Sure, I'll make a different kind of donut!

00:01:37.508 --> 00:01:40.720
"-Paint, paint, paint…
-Wow!"

00:01:40.750 --> 00:01:44.160
Here you go! It's a raspberry cream donut!

00:01:44.166 --> 00:01:47.850
Yay!!! It looks so good!

00:01:47.875 --> 00:01:50.080
Would you like more tea?

00:01:50.083 --> 00:01:51.880
Yes!

00:01:56.183 --> 00:01:59.230
Put the donut in the magic liquid and…

00:01:59.233 --> 00:02:01.200
…watch closely…

00:02:04.333 --> 00:02:07.090
It goes back to normal!

00:02:07.108 --> 00:02:10.220
I'm gonna try too!

00:02:10.266 --> 00:02:14.610
Wow! It's turning back into strawberry shortcake!

00:02:18.066 --> 00:02:22.670
Let's wash the dirty tea cups!

00:02:31.058 --> 00:02:35.900
Using the brush is annoying! I'm just gonna dump it in the water!

00:02:36.900 --> 00:02:39.880
See? It turned to chocolate cream!

00:02:39.891 --> 00:02:44.720
The color changes with hot and cold water.

00:02:44.725 --> 00:02:47.860
Put it in cold water for chocolate cake.

00:02:47.858 --> 00:02:55.950
Put it in hot water for shortcake!

00:02:59.525 --> 00:03:01.880
Blueberry cream!

00:03:07.025 --> 00:03:10.120
A half-and-half cookie!

00:03:11.491 --> 00:03:16.450
They've forgotten about the camera and are in 100% play mode…

00:03:16.450 --> 00:03:19.360
This color-changing toy was really fun!

00:03:19.358 --> 00:03:23.680
Next we're going to play with this set in the bathtub!

00:03:23.683 --> 00:03:25.720
Please try this out for yourself!

00:03:25.716 --> 00:03:28.700
"-Byebye, come watch us again!
-See ya!"

00:03:28.700 --> 00:03:32.740
Let's change into our bathing suits! Ready?

00:03:33.758 --> 00:03:37.630
Now let's go to the bathtub! Ready?

00:03:39.066 --> 00:03:41.600
"-We're here!
-Yay!"

00:03:44.041 --> 00:03:47.140
It changes color quickly!

00:03:47.150 --> 00:03:50.070
Here's your blueberry cookie!

00:03:50.100 --> 00:03:53.440
Actually, I think I want a strawberry cookie…

00:03:54.875 --> 00:03:57.480
For real?! Weirdo…

00:03:58.716 --> 00:04:02.120
Here's your strawberry cookie!

00:04:02.125 --> 00:04:04.670
Actually, I'd like a blueberry cookie!

